      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AGENT TWENTY ONE (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Elegant Ember (23.00) in a Grade 6. Has the pace to be prominent. Rates highly and will give a great sight. DANYO'S ALBIE (4) is a well performed dog and winner of 10 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (23.30). Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from seven starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. KILCOY GEM (1) ran below her best last time finishing sixth (17.13) over 300m at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Leading chance. HERE COMES SHAKA (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
